.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH kuva 1  "kuva 0.1.7" 
.SH NAME
kuva \- Scientific plotting from the command line
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBkuva\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Scientific plotting from the command line
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
kuva\-scatter(1)
Scatter plot from two numeric columns
.TP
kuva\-line(1)
Line plot from two numeric columns
.TP
kuva\-bar(1)
Bar chart from label and value columns
.TP
kuva\-histogram(1)
Histogram from a numeric column
.TP
kuva\-box(1)
Box\-and\-whisker plot grouped by a column
.TP
kuva\-violin(1)
Violin plot grouped by a column
.TP
kuva\-pie(1)
Pie or donut chart from label and value columns
.TP
kuva\-strip(1)
Strip / beeswarm plot grouped by a column
.TP
kuva\-waterfall(1)
Waterfall chart from label and delta\-value columns
.TP
kuva\-stacked\-area(1)
Stacked area chart from x, group, and y columns
.TP
kuva\-volcano(1)
Volcano plot for differential expression analysis
.TP
kuva\-manhattan(1)
Manhattan plot for GWAS results
.TP
kuva\-candlestick(1)
Candlestick / OHLC chart from open, high, low, close columns
.TP
kuva\-heatmap(1)
Heatmap from a wide matrix (first column as row labels)
.TP
kuva\-hist2d(1)
2\-D density histogram from two numeric columns
.TP
kuva\-contour(1)
Contour or filled\-contour plot from scattered x/y/z data
.TP
kuva\-dot(1)
Dot plot with size and colour encoding
.TP
kuva\-upset(1)
UpSet intersection plot from binary set\-membership columns
.TP
kuva\-chord(1)
Chord diagram from an N×N flow matrix
.TP
kuva\-sankey(1)
Sankey flow diagram from source, target, and value columns
.TP
kuva\-phylo(1)
Phylogenetic tree from a Newick string or edge list
.TP
kuva\-synteny(1)
Genome synteny ribbons from sequence and block files
.TP
kuva\-density(1)
Kernel density estimate curve from a numeric column
.TP
kuva\-ecdf(1)
Empirical cumulative distribution function (ECDF)
.TP
kuva\-qq(1)
Q\-Q plot: normal or genomic (GWAS) quantile\-quantile
.TP
kuva\-streamgraph(1)
Streamgraph (flowing stacked area with displaced baseline)
.TP
kuva\-ridgeline(1)
Ridgeline (joyplot) — stacked KDE density curves, one per group
.TP
kuva\-polar(1)
Polar coordinate scatter/line plot
.TP
kuva\-ternary(1)
Ternary (simplex) scatter plot with barycentric coordinate system
.TP
kuva\-forest(1)
Forest plot — point estimates with confidence intervals on a categorical Y\-axis
.TP
kuva\-scatter3d(1)
3D scatter plot with orthographic projection
.TP
kuva\-surface3d(1)
3D surface plot with orthographic projection
.TP
kuva\-network(1)
Network / graph diagram from an edge list or adjacency matrix
.TP
kuva\-radar(1)
Radar / spider chart — multivariate data on radial axes
.TP
kuva\-hexbin(1)
Hexbin density plot — aggregate scatter points into hexagonal bins
.TP
kuva\-treemap(1)
Treemap — tile a rectangle proportionally to values, with optional hierarchical grouping
.TP
kuva\-sunburst(1)
Sunburst chart — radial hierarchy diagram
.TP
kuva\-bump(1)
Bump chart — rank of series across discrete time points
.TP
kuva\-funnel(1)
Funnel chart — attrition / conversion through ordered stages
.TP
kuva\-rose(1)
Nightingale rose / coxcomb chart — polar bar chart
.TP
kuva\-slope(1)
Slope chart — paired before/after comparisons on two axes
.TP
kuva\-lollipop(1)
Lollipop chart — dot\-and\-stem alternative to bar charts
.TP
kuva\-raincloud(1)
Raincloud plot — half\-violin + box + jittered raw points
.TP
kuva\-mosaic(1)
Mosaic / Marimekko chart — two\-way contingency table
.TP
kuva\-waffle(1)
Waffle chart — proportional grid of filled squares
.TP
kuva\-pyramid(1)
Population pyramid — back\-to\-back horizontal bar chart
.TP
kuva\-roc(1)
ROC curve — receiver operating characteristic
.TP
kuva\-pr(1)
Precision\-recall curve
.TP
kuva\-survival(1)
Kaplan\-Meier survival curve
.TP
kuva\-horizon(1)
Horizon chart — stacked folded time\-series
.TP
kuva\-parallel(1)
Parallel coordinates plot — multivariate comparison
.TP
kuva\-venn(1)
Venn diagram — 2–4 set overlaps
.TP
kuva\-calendar(1)
Calendar heatmap — GitHub\-style contribution grid
.TP
kuva\-quiver(1)
Quiver plot — 2\-D vector field rendered as arrows
.TP
kuva\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.1.7
